<B>Company Information:</B><BR>
Visteon Multimedia Systems is a leading-edge innovator of breakthrough aftermarket and OE automotive electronics and telematic products.  Utilizing more that 100 years of experience, Visteon combines an enterprising nature, consumer insights and technological expertise to offer integrated systems solutions that make customers successful.  CES 2000 will witness and even stronger Visteon customer focus and commitment through the technological innovations displayed.  Visteon will feature breakthroughs including I.C.E.S. (delivering mobile connectivity to the internet and email via voice prompts), NavMate Navigation System (Visteon's branded navigational technology), Rear Seat Entertainment, CD6 Music System and more!

Visteon will be at the Sands Expo Center, Booth 18423.  Come see the innovations. . .each offers advanced technological solutions that reach into your lifestyle and simply make it better! <BR>


